Another data point that seems very peculiar to me… 
This is from a brand new just opened never domain joined just fully updated by
MS and DELL – Latitude 5540 W11 notebook 
[cid:image001.png@01DA4E1F.73D39610] 
Why 2 Recovery Partitions on a factory install??? 
And no I do not know what it was like before any MS updates to the delivered
system were done. 
Cal
